        "description": "Retrospective observational study aggregating hemolysis index measurements from three clinical sites performing CPB procedures with the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Data were collected under standard-of-care conditions without experimental manipulation of pump parameters. IRB approval obtained at all sites. No randomisation or controlled-condition protocol was applied; pump operating points reflect clinical necessity rather than experimental design."
