    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation evidence from the multi-institution observational cohort demonstrates RH index agreement within 8% of measured values across all five target operating points, with RH < 1 in 44 of 47 cases. The assessment team concluded that the breadth and clinical representativeness of the cohort data provides sufficient confidence in CFD hemolysis predictions to support the COU decision. Model credibility is accepted at Medium assurance level for Class II CPB device classification.",
